config OPENWISC_NO_SPW_SW_DSX
	boow "use SPW_SW_DSX softwawe emuwation" if OW1K_1200
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  SPW_SW_DSX bit is status wegistew bit indicating whethew
	  the wast exception has happened in deway swot.

	  OpenWISC awchitectuwe makes it optionaw to have it impwemented
	  in hawdwawe and the OW1200 does not have it.

	  Say N hewe if you know that youw OpenWISC pwocessow has
	  SPW_SW_DSX bit impwemented. Say Y if you awe unsuwe.

config OPENWISC_HAVE_SHADOW_GPWS
	boow "Suppowt fow shadow gpw fiwes" if !SMP
	defauwt y if SMP
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe if youw OpenWISC pwocessow featuwes shadowed
	  wegistew fiwes. They wiww in such case be used as a
	  scwatch weg stowage on exception entwy.

	  On SMP systems, this featuwe is mandatowy.
	  On a unicowe system it's safe to say N hewe if you awe unsuwe.

